history.content:
EECS 127 would prepare you much more for 189 than 110 would, as 127 covers more linear algebra applications. If you're going to take it P/NP, then it should be low workload anyways.

---------


Also, just check on the EECS P/NP deadlines. If you haven't fulfilled all the graduation requirements that may be a bit stricter than is ideal for your situation.
